      "content": "it just feels like i'm just dragging this version of myself around. a version that's broken and empty. i don't see the point in trying to \"manage\" it or \"find a path\" when the path is just more of this. honestly, it sounds more like peace than everything else does. maybe there's no point in trying to fix something that's just fundamentally gone.",
